%N A140944 Triangle T(d,n) read by rows, the n-th term of the d-th differences of the Jacobsthal sequence A001045.
%C A140944 A variant of the triangle A140503, now including the diagonal.
%C A140944 Since the diagonal contains zeros, rows sums are those of A140503.
%F A140944 T(d,n)=T(d-1,n+1)-T(d-1,n). T(0,n)=A001045(n).
%F A140944 T(d,n) = (2^n - 2^d*(-1)^(d+n))/3, for d >= n >= 0. - _Jianing Song_, Aug 11 2022
